Several Jubilee lawmakers have urged NASA co-principals Musalia Mudavadi and Moses Wetang’ula to join the Government. The MPs said the two have remained in the cold for too long, and should embrace President Uhuru Kenyatta. Navakholo MP Emmanuel Wangwe, while speaking during the burial of Ebushibo Primary School pupil struck by lightning, asked the ANC and Ford-K leaders to follow Wiper leader Kalonzo Musyoka’s example. ALSO READ:

